<BR><A HREF="http://www.krunch.net/spiritslammer">Clan Spiritslammer</A></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#313532><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ualvimar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Alvimar</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_ball.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Traveller of Underfoot</span><br>  Posts: 203<br> <font color=#CC9900>(3/9/01 8:56:02 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Need opinions - Last Piece Rule</span><hr size=1> /agree Kruunch<br>
