<br>
If you do not want to get all your pieces and just want one item, roll with everyone else or work something out with the other people of your class on the raid.  Nothing is stopping someone from talking to the other people on the raid and working out a deal.  I have seen druids not partake in the bp roll because that was the last piece someone wanted from the planes.  Was not part of the loot rules, it was something they worked out themselves.<br>
<br>
